
Tests on the stout smearing routines

test01_omega_matrices.c         Checks of the computation of the X matrix with
                                diagonal matrices

test02_smear_n1.c               Check of n=1 smearing agains a reference
                                configuration

test03_smear_n2.c               Check of n=2 smearing agains a reference
                                configuration

test04_smear_n3.c               Check of n=3 smearing agains a reference
                                configuration

test05_unsmearing_intrinsics.c  Checks of the unsmearing intrinsic functions

test06_unsmearing_1.c           Basic check on force unsmearing routine

test07_smeared_field_cycling.c  Checks for how smear_fields() and unsmear_fields()
                                behave

test08_xi_matrix_test.c         Checks of the computation of the lambda field

Note that the 8th test is currently not implemented for NPROC > 1.
